This place looks a little plain from the outside but the interior is really nice, well decorated and very comfortable!   They have an awesome wine selection and the food is really good! The eggplant appetizer was AWESOME. They have an extensive pizza menu as well as a lot of regular entrees.  If you live in chandler, Mesa or tempe I would recommend giving it a try!

