This place is wonderful. They have wonderful and welcoming instructors who are very focused on making sure everyone in their class is practicing properly and correctly. They really seem to care that you have the best practice possible. Each of the rooms that they hold classes in have a glass wall that faces a beautiful pond that is surrounded by lush greenery and adorably happy ducks. The scenery really adds to my practice. I've never had a bad experience here during my consistent months of attendance.

